topThird.description: Applications for Commit the Change concluded in mid-October for the 2021-22 school year. Stay tuned on our website and social media to get updates for when we re-open applications in the future!

middleThird.topDescription: We work with non-profit organizations throughout the school year (September 2021 - June 2022) on a software project that has a meaningful, positive impact and will be a good learning experience for our team.
